HOW TO RUN

We should note that the operation on Lenss1 should always be started first, the client also needs to
be started on Lenss1

Step1 On Lenss1:
1. make
2. ./fbsd server.sh masterServer    /*start master server first*/

Step2 on Lenss3:
1. make
2. ./fbsd server.sh server1         /*start 1st slave server*/

Step3 on Lenss4:
1. make
2. ./fbsd server.sh server2         /*start 2nd slave server*/

Step4 on Lenss1:
3. ./fbc <username>                 /*start your client*/

    ////////////////////////////////////////////////////
    PLEASE DO NOT INCLUDE SPACE OR '~' IN YOUR USERNAME
    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////
    
4. Command mode 
   LIST  -> show all users;
   JOIN  -> join others;
   LEAVE -> leave others;
   CHAT -> INTO Chat Mode
   
   /////////////////////////////////////////////////////
   PLEASE DO NOT SHUTDOWN CLIENT IN COMMAND MODE.
   OTHERWISE YOU MAY NEED RESTART SERVER TO LOG IN AGAIN
   //////////////////////////////////////////////////////
   
5.CHATMODE
Enter everything you want
use ctrl + c to quit
